700877f-a.title: Bronx: Fordham Road (East) - Bathgate Avenue
700877f-a.text:
E. Fordham Road, south side, west from Bathgate to Washington
Avenues, siowing Theodore Roosevelt High school. The view is from
Lorillard Place.
May 12, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
